'''洞鬣狗'''（学名：{{lang|la|''Crocuta crocuta spelaea''}}）是[[斑鬣狗|斑鬣狗]]已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的一個[[亞種|亞種]]<ref name="rholand2005">Rohland, N, Pollack, JL, Nagel, D, Beauval, C, Airvaux J, Paabo, S & Hofreiter, M, 2005. The population history of extant and extinct hyenas. ''[[Molecular_Biology_and_Evolution|Molecular Biology and Evolution]],''. 22: 2435-2443.</ref>，分佈於[[伊比利半島|伊比利半島]]至[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]東部<ref name="Gnawed Bones tell Tales">Summerill, Lynette; [http://www.asu.edu/research/researchmagazine/2003Summer/sum03p34-37.pdf Gnawed Bones tell Tales] {{Wayback|url=http://www.asu.edu/research/researchmagazine/2003Summer/sum03p34-37.pdf |date=20201024011324 }}, Summer 2003, ''ASU Research''</ref>。雖然洞鬣狗最初因前後肢的不同而被描述成獨立的[[物種|物種]]，但[[基因|基因]]分析顯示洞鬣狗與斑鬣狗並沒有[[DNA|DNA]]的明顯分別。<ref name="crocuta">{{cite web | url = http://www.oeaw.ac.at/kfq/hyaenas/thesis.pdf | title = Comparison of Crocuta crocutacrocuta and Crocuta crocutaspelaea through computertomography | work = Dockner, Martin | publisher = Department of Paleontology, University of Vienna | accessdate = 2008-01-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110522090237/http://www.oeaw.ac.at/kfq/hyaenas/thesis.pdf | archivedate = 2011-05-22 }}</ref>除了洞鬣狗的[[化石|化石]]外，一些[[石洞壁畫|石洞壁畫]]亦有發現洞鬣狗。洞鬣狗於約2萬至1萬年前的[[冰河時期|冰河時期]]末滅絕，原因仍然未知，但多半認為是[[氣候變遷|氣候變遷]]以及與其他[[掠食者|掠食者]]競爭造成<ref name="stiner">C. Stiner, Mary (2004) [http://www.u.arizona.edu/~mstiner/pdf/Stiner2004a.pdf Comparative ecology and taphonomy of spotted hyenas, humans, and wolves in Pleistocene Italy] {{Wayback|url=http://www.u.arizona.edu/~mstiner/pdf/Stiner2004a.pdf |date=20190508135925 }}, ''Revue de Paléobiologie, Genève''. (December 2004) 23 (2) : 771-785. ISSN 0253-6730</ref><ref name="varela2010.1">Varela, S., Lobo, J. M., Rodríguez, J. and Batra, P. (2010). [http://paleobiogeography.org/uploads/assets/1_Varela_et_al_QSR_2010.pdf Were the Late Pleistocene climatic changes responsible for the disappearance of the European spotted hyena populations?] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426071500/http://paleobiogeography.org/uploads/assets/1_Varela_et_al_QSR_2010.pdf |date=2012-04-26 }} ''Quaternary Science Reviews'', 29: 2027-2035.</ref>。

== 描述 ==
洞鬣狗的體型遠大於現存於非洲的斑鬣狗，體重可達 {{convert|102|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref name="meloro2007">Meloro, C., 2007. [http://www.fedoa.unina.it/1935/1/Meloro_Scienze_Terra.pdf Plio-Pleistocene large carnivores from the Italian peninsula: functional morphology and macroecology] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fedoa.unina.it/1935/1/Meloro_Scienze_Terra.pdf |date=20170517014331 }}. Ph.D. Thesis, Univ. Naples Federico II.</ref>，[[掌骨|掌骨]]與[[跖骨|跖骨]]也較短而粗壯，[[肱骨|肱骨]]與[[股骨|股骨]]則較長<ref name="kurten1968">Kurtén, Björn (1968). ''Pleistocene mammals of Europe''. Weidenfeld and Nicolson. pp. 69-72.</ref>，這是為了生活於和斑鬣狗不同的環境所做出的適應<ref name="dockner2006">Dockner, M., 2006. Comparison of ''Crocuta crocuta crocuta'' and ''Crocuta crocuta spelaea'' through computer tomography. Ph.D. Thesis, Univ. Vienna, Austria.</ref>。與斑鬣狗同樣為[[兩性異形|兩性異形]]，雌性鬣狗體型大於雄性<ref name="diedrich&zak">DIEDRICH, C.G. & ŽÁK, K. 2006. [http://www.geology.cz/bulletin/fulltext/bullgeosci200604237.pdf Prey deposits and den sites of the Upper Pleistocene hyena Crocuta crocuta spelaea (Goldfuss, 1823) in horizontal and vertical caves of the Bohemian Karst (Czech Republic)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.geology.cz/bulletin/fulltext/bullgeosci200604237.pdf |date=20141129162542 }}. ''Bulletin of Geosciences'' 81(4), 237–276 (25 figures). Czech Geological Survey, Prague. ISSN 1214-1119.</ref>。由一些[[石洞壁畫|石洞壁畫]]可知，洞鬣狗和斑鬣狗一樣具有斑點<ref name="spassov2004">Spassov N.; Stoytchev T. 2004. [http://www.nmnhs.com/downloads/pdfs/historia-naturalis-bulgarica/2004/016-159-166.pdf The presence of cave hyaena (Crocuta crocuta spelaea) in the Upper Palaeolithic rock art of Europe] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nmnhs.com/downloads/pdfs/historia-naturalis-bulgarica/2004/016-159-166.pdf |date=20120415101508 }}. ''Historia naturalis bulgarica'', 16: 159-166.</ref>。

對於洞鬣狗的社交習性只知很少。一般接受牠們都是生活在洞穴中。現時未有顯示牠們是成群生活或是獨自生活的，但[[更新世|更新世]]環境似乎不可能有成群生活的[[動物|動物]]。<ref name="crocuta"/>

=== 食性 ===
洞鬣狗像現今的[[鬣狗|鬣狗]]般會在巢穴積存獵物的骨頭及角，供日後食用或玩耍，但這些骨頭並不清楚是屬於腐屍的或是被獵殺的動物。就[[波西米亞|波西米亞]]岩洞內遺骸的研究顯示，[[普氏野馬|普氏野馬]]明顯是牠們的獵物，約佔16-51%。洞鬣狗最大的獵物是[[披毛犀|披毛犀]]，在很多洞鬣狗的巢穴中都有發現牠們的骨頭及[[頭顱骨|頭顱骨]]。在一些區域，披毛犀佔其獵物的25-30%。[[馴鹿|馴鹿]]亦是另一個重要的食物來源，約佔7-15%。[[長角野牛|長角野牛]]及[[馬鹿|馬鹿]]分別佔1-6%及3%，其他的亦包括了[[愛爾蘭麋鹿|愛爾蘭麋鹿]]、[[臆羚|臆羚]]及[[野山羊|野山羊]]則只有少於3%。<ref name="spelaea">{{cite web| url = http://64.233.183.104/search?q=cache:TH2j9N58LoQJ:nts1.cgu.cz/bulletin/contents/2006/vol81no4/237_diedrich.pdf+Crocuta+spelaea&hl=en&ct=clnk&cd=13| title = Prey deposits and den sites of the Upper Pleistocene hyena Crocuta crocuta spelaea (Goldfuss, 1823)in horizontal and vertical caves of the Bohemian Karst| work = Cajusg. Diedrich & Karelzák| publisher = | accessdate = 2008-01-20}}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

一般相信洞鬣狗是將[[洞熊|洞熊]][[骨骼|骨骼]]拆解及破壞的元兇。這麼大型的腐肉是洞鬣狗的重要食物，尤其是在[[冬季|冬季]]當食物短缺時。[[穴獅|穴獅]]、[[狼|狼]]及[[貂熊|貂熊]]的遺骸亦於洞鬣狗的巢穴發現。另外有證據顯示洞鬣狗有時會[[同類相食|同類相食]]的。<ref name="spelaea"/>

== 與人科的關係 ==
[[File:20,000_Year_Old_Cave_Paintings_Hyena.png|right]]內的繪畫]]
有證據指洞鬣狗會偷取[[尼安德特人|尼安德特人]]的獵物，而牠們亦會為洞穴而競爭，並會取代對方擁有該洞穴。在洞鬣狗的骨頭積存中亦發現有大量的[[人科|人科]]骨頭，包括尼安德特人的。現今[[人類|人類]]亦會與洞鬣狗並存，估計他們之間亦有相似的關係。

